# Lagerverwaltung App


A privat project to master in PHP and MySQL and Database Design.

The project Lagerverwaltung (conves_lvw2) is a Web App to manage the a stock of a company.
It should include the following requirements:

- Database to store (maschines, paint, product number, status, user name, pw)
- Login page
- categories page, list all categories (Verbrauchsmaterialien, Farben, Abdeckmaterialien, Maschinen, Werkzeug)  
- Farben/ Lacke category page
  list all items with there properties (Hersteller, Farbart, Farbton, Farbnummer, Counter)
- Abdeckmaterial category page
  list all items with there properties (Bezeichnung, Counter)
- Maschine category page
  list all items with there properties (Bezeichnung, Lagerstatus)
- Werkzeuge category page
  list all items with there properties (Bezeichnung, Counter)
- Verbrauchsmaterialien category page
  list all items with there properties (Bezeichner)

- Hinzug√ºgen item page

The project is in process but is currently on hold because of other projects.
